=================================================================
  HeteroFloodGNN  —  Inference Time Benchmark
=================================================================
  Device  : cuda  (NVIDIA A100 80GB PCIe MIG 3g.40gb)
  Warmup  : 10 runs
  Timed   : 50 runs
=================================================================

  [Model 1]  n_1d=  17  n_2d= 3716  hidden=64  wl_prev=2
            in_1d=36  in_2d=26

  Parameters: 374,616

  Output  →  1D shape: (17, 4)   2D shape: (3716, 4)

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  Full forward pass (1D + 2D combined)   │
  │  Mean  :    9.907 ms              │
  │  Std   :    0.850 ms              │
  │  Min   :    9.038 ms              │
  │  Max   :   12.407 ms              │
  │  p95   :   10.774 ms              │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Estimated per-head inference time (proportional to node count):
    1D nodes (  17 / 3733 = 0.5%)  →  ~0.0451 ms
    2D nodes ( 3716 / 3733 = 99.5%)  →  ~9.8615 ms

  [Model 2]  n_1d= 198  n_2d= 4299  hidden=96  wl_prev=10
            in_1d=44  in_2d=34

  Parameters: 807,584

  Output  →  1D shape: (198, 4)   2D shape: (4299, 4)

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  Full forward pass (1D + 2D combined)   │
  │  Mean  :    9.240 ms              │
  │  Std   :    0.330 ms              │
  │  Min   :    9.103 ms              │
  │  Max   :   11.469 ms              │
  │  p95   :    9.370 ms              │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Estimated per-head inference time (proportional to node count):
    1D nodes ( 198 / 4497 = 4.4%)  →  ~0.4068 ms
    2D nodes ( 4299 / 4497 = 95.6%)  →  ~8.8331 ms

=================================================================
  SUMMARY  —  Inference Times (mean ± std over 50 runs)
=================================================================
  Variant                          Mean (ms)   Std (ms)   p95 (ms)
  -------------------------------------------------------------
  Model 1  —  1D nodes                0.0451     0.0039     0.0491
  Model 1  —  2D nodes                9.8615     0.8461    10.7251
  Model 2  —  1D nodes                0.4068     0.0145     0.4125
  Model 2  —  2D nodes                8.8331     0.3156     8.9570

  Full forward pass (1D + 2D together):
  Model 1  —  full pass                9.907      0.850     10.774
  Model 2  —  full pass                9.240      0.330      9.370
=================================================================

  NOTE: 1D/2D per-head times are proportional estimates.
        The GNN processes both node types in a single fused
        forward pass; they cannot be isolated without
        architectural changes.
=================================================================
